title: Cooking Under Pressure
itunes:title: Cooking Under Pressure
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Kate and Leisha get talking about the perfect salad, refreshing summer drink recipes, and the predestined reality that neither of them are that skilled at cooking. But maybe with some practice they can beat the odds. Maybe.
